OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start, but
OL,6,Fcloud will gradually build with some
OL,7,Fshowery outbreaks of rain developing
OL,8,Fby lunchtime. This afternoon will then
OL,9,Fsee a band of more persistent rain
OL,10,Farriving from the west accompanied by
OL,11,Fa brisk breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA wet evening and night to
OL,14,Fcome with the rain heavy and
OL,15,Fpersistent at times, especially over
OL,16,Fthe hills. Windy initially, although
OL,17,Feasing later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
