OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA wet start, especially in the
OL,6,Feast. Rain will begin to clear from
OL,7,Fthe west though with a mix of sunshine
OL,8,Fand a few showers for the afternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,11,FStaying unsettled with a mixture of
OL,12,Fsunshine and showers on Tuesday and
OL,13,FWednesday, before turning wet and
OL,14,Fwindy on Thursday. Temperatures around
OL,15,For a little below average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
